ve suggests. I=E2=80=99m not even that worried. Why? Because I=E2=80=99ve d=
iversified my portfolio with uncorrelated alternative assets. That helps me=
 protect my portfolio without sacrificing alpha. And there=E2=80=99s one al=
ternative that=E2=80=99s caught my eye.
It has a -.04 correlation to equities according to Citi. Plus, when inflati=
on is over 3%, its prices increase by 36% historically=E2=80=94 more than 5=
x better than real estate and gold. So it=E2=80=99s no wonder Deloitte repo=
rted 85% of wealth managers want to offer it to clients.=C2=A0
Spoiler Alert: it=E2=80=99s Contemporary art.=C2=A0
