#1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">This same =
pattern plays out over and over, across industries. Companies rise and fall=
, but humanity progresses.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">The example Byrne provided &#8=
211; the Dot Com Bubble &#8211; is a canonical example. The swarm tried a m=
illion things, most of which failed, some of which (like Amazon and Google)=
 became wildly successful. Even the failures contributed to bringing the wo=
